      "id": "pgQHU-ePNS8",
      "user": "Alex",
      "text": "To wrap this up, let's look at one final \"quality of life\" improvement. Since json-server is a local API, it responds fast, but in a real-world app with a slow database, users might double-click the \"Post\" button and create duplicate comments.\n",
